{"type": "article", "id": 9829, "title": "Fujifilm 无反相机 X-T10", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-21T07:08:30Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 11, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235509Tmuo8ehIBAPqxwr6.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\tFujifilm 最近为 X 系列新添无反相机 X-T10。比起 X-T1 来看，X-T10 更加小巧精致，重量仅为 381g，新增了弹出式闪光灯设计，采用银黑配色，整体风格复古优雅。材料上使用铝镁合金，机顶上设有三个铝合金转盘，使用者可以通过简单的拨杆快速切换成全自动拍摄模式。这个系列将在今年 6 月发售。<a href=\"http://www.fujifilm.com/products/digital_cameras/x/fujifilm_x_t10/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看详细信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235507OBiTcy8VHK4QzY9s.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66538462\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235508V94cQj2WG7BKTPLf.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.53691275\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235508Ajxao9Ru1mhqKvOD.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.53691275\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}